                            <button class="px-5 py-2.5 border border-blue-300 dark:border-blue-700 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/30 transition" onclick="requestDataExport()">
                                <i class="fas fa-download ml-1"></i> تصدير البيانات
