                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-pink-100 dark:bg-pink-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">
                            <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
                        </div>
                        اللغة والمظهر
                    </h2>
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
